				<td colspan="2"><span>First.... learn to pull in OOW and wos mostly. Get that pulling skill up. Do this with guildies... b/c they will not mind you learning to pull more. Those skills will be needed later.
<br />

<br />
Your gloves-go with iron gauntlets of ruin.<a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30640">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30640</a>
<br />
Your neck-I seem to having your problem too. I can not seem to find a good neck item. collar of vigor is good though (drops from a newborn murkglider in DS). has some saves on it too.
<br />

<br />
Your ring- Try getting a maze runner ring <a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31272">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=31272</a>
<br />

<br />
mask- maze runner mask <a target="_new" href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30523">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=30523</a></span></td>
